            Ixx, Iyy, Izz, and Ixz are given in slug-ft^2

            Moments of inertia are defined as follows:

            Ixx = Integral((y^2+z^2),dm)
            Iyy = Integral((x^2+z^2),dm)
            Izz = Integral((x^2+y^2),dm)
            Ixy = Integral(x*y,dm)
            Ixz = Integral(x*z,dm)
            Iyz = Integral(y*z,dm)
        -->
        <ixx unit="SLUG*FT2">   9496.0 </ixx>
        <iyy unit="SLUG*FT2">  55814.0 </iyy>
